	<transcript sound="sound1"><![CDATA[One crucial measure to protect food from contamination is to keep your hands clean.<br /><br />Adequate facilities need to be provided for washing hands. Can you identify what facilities are required to wash hands?<br /><br />Scroll through the images at the bottom right of the screen. Drag and drop them into either of the two categories.]]></transcript>

